Syntax: bond mastery

At maximum rank (5) in any track, you can unlock mastery, which grants
your bonded weapon a special passive ability that activates periodically
during combat.

  Edge Mastery: "Bloodthirst"
    Your blade hungers for blood. It occasionally lashes out with a bonus
    slash attack against your opponent, dealing damage based on your
    damroll. ~8% chance per combat tick.

  Guard Mastery: "Aegis Ward"
    Your blade projects a shimmering ward. It periodically heals you for
    5% of your maximum HP during combat. ~10% chance per combat tick.
    Out of combat, the blade hums with protective resonance.

  Keen Mastery: "Deep Wound"
    Your blade whispers of weak points. It occasionally inflicts a
    bleeding wound on foes, applying a weakening effect. ~6% chance
    per combat tick.

  Spirit Mastery: "Living Steel"
    Your blade breathes with living energy. It periodically restores
    4% of max HP and 4% of max mana, both in and out of combat.
    ~8% chance per tick.

Mastery persists through death, track changes (if you re-achieve rank 5),
and logout. It is a permanent upgrade once activated.

